cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.CE, cs.NE 

This paper involves the application of machine learning methods to predict gene ontology terms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DB (Databases), cs.CE (Computational Biology and Bioinformatics), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
